      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under version control with documented test suite; all project requirements for SQA at MRL 2 satisfied.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 employed under ISO 9001-compliant QMS. Version control via Git with tagged release. Regression test suite of 47 cases executed with zero critical failures. Satisfies MRL 2 SQA project requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
