      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental dataset provides inlet flow rates (2–8 L/min), rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM), and fluid properties (bovine blood, 37°C). Temperature and hematocrit recorded per test. Boundary conditions directly mapped to CFD inputs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
