      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) must agree with experimental measurements within ±25% across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared against 5 experimental operating points. Maximum deviation 18.3%, mean absolute error 11.7%. All comparisons within acceptance band. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed for all tolerance variants tested."
    },
    {
